@jchervinsky 5/ what I haven't yet dug into as much is whether/how exactly the $$ is pooled for Kin and whether when purchasers exited (spent or used) Kin how that might affect the analysis, even assuming we're in jurisdiction where horizontal test will apply. Thanks for flagging!üòÄ

@jchervinsky 4/ whereas the "narrow" vertical view focuses on whether purchaser's profits/losses are directly correlated w/seller's profits/losses. I believe only the 9th circuit follows this. So you're likely right that if filed in, eg SDNY, horizontal approach would apply

@jchervinsky 3/ vertical, which focuses on relationship btw purchaser & seller. Even w/in this there is a split. The "broad" vertical view focuses on whether purchaser's success depends on seller's expertise (5th and 11th circuit follow)

@ranreichman @prestonjbyrne Often there will be 2nd or 3rd superseding indictments in the life of a case that will add charges as new facts or evidence developed (or new witnesses come forward/flip). Not saying that will happen here but it‚Äôs quite common.
7/ just some prelim thoughts here, obviously lots can change in investigating and litigating case and ultimate sentence up to sentencing judge

6/ If plea, expect far lower guidelines recommended prison range, ie single digits, bc w/plea parties may choose not to seek certain enhancements, agree on loss amount, and deft gets -3 levels for accepting responsibility
5/Bottom line: if goes to trial expect govt to argue high loss amount, # victims, etc. so guidelines range may approach 11-14 yrs depending on govt establishing loss currently alleged

4/ In this case amount of $ loss is what‚Äôs going to drive recommended guidelines prison term assuming conviction. Current indictment appears to allege approx $154m loss which adds +26 levels, though this could grow in superseding indictments (loss enhancements cap out at $550m)

3/ Guidelines recommend # months in prison by combining prior crim history (here I) with offense level (here 7 for fraud) though level enhanced for e.g. # victims, amount of $ loss, complex or overseas conduct, etc. Allegation Theranos defrauded govt agencies could enhance more
2/ Stat max is 20 yrs meaning judge can‚Äôt go higher. But what drives actual prison term are these sentencing guidelines https://t.co/SAF1oDEYGD
